麻里奈","body":"是嗎，原來是這樣。\n我原本還以為，PAREO應該很愛去主題樂園的說","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev158-me2-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":34}],"windowDisplayName":"PAREO","body":"其實這是我第一次去。\n所以真的覺得很興奮，\n回到家後也馬上倒頭就睡～","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":34,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":34,"voiceId":"ev158-me2-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"呵呵，你玩得這麼開心啊。\n之後還有機會再和RAS的大家一起去玩就好了","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev158-me2-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":34}],"windowDisplayName":"PAREO","body":"是的！\n如果成行，以後再請聽我分享！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":34,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":34,"voiceId":"ev158-me2-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"當然可以啊～","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"m